{"tid":1639791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］雙十賀佢老母","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:08:11.000Z","uid":310037,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"142b694aac76962c88f44712374f814f620e0632","tid":1639791,"uid":310037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P27PgTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP27PgTK.jpg&h=65edf446&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLmMi65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLmMi65.jpg&h=758e0022&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqh35M6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faqh35M6.jpg&h=5e7dbfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實大家雙十諗住點Connect臺灣同胞？<br />\n👆🏽圖係同臺灣朋友嘅討論。可歸納成以下幾點：<br />\n1.咪L用青天白日（滿地紅）<br />\n🇹🇼係國際上好多都覺得係中華民國，你望下人地點講都知民國個朵唔多好聽，揮呢支人地會好老尷。<br />\n記住民國唔代表臺灣，就等於日本皇軍唔等於日本，而且支持香港嘅都唔撐賣民黨，舉🇹🇼會被屈成撐國民黨，要政治正確啊。<br />\n建議用臺灣旗（見附圖），雖然係綠營，但點都好過承認賣民黨。歡迎巴絲發揮創意（拜<br />\n<br />\n2.「島嶼天光」係首選歌<br />\n雖然係閩南話好難短時間學，但係係人地太陽花個Theme，係唔少撐港臺灣人眼中同「願榮光」有過之而無不及，而且HOCC都有唱過，唔係唔撐啊。<br />\n如果唔掂可以揀「台灣的心聲」或「美麗島」，國語好搞好多。「台灣的心聲」可能connect到更多人，人地世博都唱呢隻，藍綠都喜。咩「民國國歌」「國旗歌」，不了<br />\n島嶼天光：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iV8JDbtXZm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiV8JDbtXZm4&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=d6382013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iV8JDbtXZm4</a><br />\nHOCC版：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ocahk2nUabM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Focahk2nUabM&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=b4face26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ocahk2nUabM</a><br />\n台灣的心聲：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uNXS9y-QY04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuNXS9y-QY04&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=ea345a20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uNXS9y-QY04</a><br />\n美麗島：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bb2jXvj9CAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbb2jXvj9CAc&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=fd34d830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bb2jXvj9CAc</a><br />\n<br />\n3.英文姐未贏架！！<br />\n民調無錯超左幾條街，但侵侵當年都係啦，今日咪幫緊大家搞支爆同抗共。<br />\n雖然似pt1，但因為太重要。❌🇹🇼❌🇹🇼❌🇹🇼。人地發大財造勢都係fig🇹🇼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwdCqQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwdCqQX.jpg&h=7e465cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記住英文姐先係我地嘅同伴。<br />\n<br />\nPS：臺灣人都有自己嘅仗要打，人地政治生態比我地知嘅複雜幾倍，咪搞到人老尷啊。<br />\n兩岸同胞齊抗共啊屌<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n天滅中共"},{"pid":"018a2dbbfa217260a1b9d9aaca3aee0deadb7f1f","tid":1639791,"uid":310037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁，求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465355b0a64552ab6aaa751480ed8660beed6159","tid":1639791,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"p牌手動正評"},{"pid":"c731e52a2d4717ccfc044e3c3ded626b84ad2445","tid":1639791,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"03512157beca2c5b183c6f80cf8c491321e9d108","tid":1639791,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"78c89e07575e1aa5048fee8616ce7fbe80e70c23","tid":1639791,"uid":768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:32:26.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7e381d6575050fbbe0f1aa23d554c8b02dffeff6","tid":1639791,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"da08ff3c5dbf324fb187e84d911ce94874b804c7","tid":1639791,"uid":282249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi